00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:53,400
 And I'm sure that's the case for some of us here tonight.

180
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:58,180
 And the reason for that is because deconstruction

181
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:01,180
 is notoriously difficult to understand

