 named Jacques Derrida in the 1960s.

187
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:14,620
 He was a young adult himself,

188
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:16,360
 and he created this concept

189
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:19,520
 that even he was unwilling to summarize

190
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,600
 when asked how to explain it

191
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,760
 because it is annoyingly nuanced.

192
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,800
 Just take my word for it.

193
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,120
 If you want more information,

194
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,440
 you can come talk to me down to the front

