 we assume that means a really bad thing.

222
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:34,180
 And yet, I actually think within doubt,

223
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:36,600
 there's a really great opportunity.

224
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,580
 So let me explain it to you like this.

225
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:42,440
 When Brooke and I were in the market to buy a house

226
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,720
 after first moving here to Dallas,

227
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,900
 we knew that we wanted to buy a place

228
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,940
 that needed some renovations.

229
00:09:47,940 --> 00:09:48,780
 We knew it.

230
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:52,140
 We wanted to invest in a property, increase its value.

231
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:53,620
 And so as we searched the market,

232
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:55,260
 we knew we need to find a place

233
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:57,300
 that is requiring some renovation.

234
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:59,800
 Now, when we bought our house,

235
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:02,180
 the house we bought fit the bill.

