00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,380
 Do you think we walked in

238
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:08,660
 and just started swinging hammers all over the place?

239
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:10,980
 No, that would have been very bad

240
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:13,900
 because as we did a careful evaluation of the property,

241
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:17,520
 we realized, man, there are certain things here

242
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,460
 that are in great shape,

243
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:23,460
 but there are other things here that do require attention.

244
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:25,180
 Upon inspection, there were certain things

245
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:28,680
 that inspired our confidence to leave them as is,

246
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:31,140
 but there were other things that upon inspection

247
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:34,500
 inspired our concern that needed to be addressed.

248
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:37,220
 That's how we have to approach our faith.

249
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:41,440
 We have to consider as we carefully evaluate

250
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,380
 what areas of our faith are great as they are.

251
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,720
 We don't need to touch them in the slightest.

252
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:51,020
 And yet what other areas may feel,

253
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:56,020
 may feel somewhat out of date behind the times

254
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:59,340
 as if we potentially outgrown them.

255
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:03,820
 You see, the beautiful thing about doubt

256
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:08,000
 is it's not a sign that Christianity is flawed.

257
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:11,680
 A doubt is a sign that our understanding

258
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,220
 of Christianity is flawed.

259
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:16,060
 If you're here and you're wrestling with doubt,

260
00:11:16,060 --> 00:11:18,380
 it's not an issue with Christ,

261
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:21,460
 it's an issue in your understanding of who Christ is,

262
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:23,180
 which is actually really encouraging news

263
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:26,180
 because it means that God, He is just as unsearchable,

